UNITED STATES of America, Plaintiff-Appellee, v. Nicholas LINDSEY, Defendant-Appellant. No. 14-10004 United States Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Filed February 3, 2017

D.C. No. 2:ll-cr-00217-LDG-CWH-l

Before: Susan P. Graber,* Ronald M. Gould, and Michelle T. Friedland, Circuit Judges.

After oral argument in this case, and our former opinion and memorandum disposition filed June 28, 2016, and after the petition for rehearing or rehearing en banc was filed on August 19, 2016, Judge Graber on January 26, 2017, replaced Judge Noonan on this panel.

ORDER

The Defendant-Appellant’s petition for rehearing is GRANTED. The prior opinion and memorandum disposition filed June 28, 2016, are withdrawn. A substitute opinion and substitute memorandum disposition shall be filed in due course.
